# Style Guide - Intellectual Vitality

This document serves as the reference for the "Intellectual Vitality" design system implemented in the application.

## 1. Color Palette

The palette uses a serious, academic foundation with high-energy accents.

| Color Name | Hex Code | CSS Variable | Tailwind Utility | Usage |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Oxford Blue** | `#1D2D50` | `--color-oxford-blue` | `bg-oxford-blue`, `text-oxford-blue` | Primary backgrounds, Headers, Professionalism. |
| **Charcoal** | `#131515` | `--color-charcoal` | `bg-charcoal`, `text-charcoal` | Alternative dark background, High contrast text. |
| **Off-White/Bone** | `#FBFBFB` | `--color-off-white` | `bg-off-white`, `text-off-white` | Cards, Sections, Backgrounds (easier on eyes than pure white). |
| **Electric Saffron** | `#F3CA40` | `--color-electric-saffron` | `bg-electric-saffron`, `text-electric-saffron` | Accents, Buttons, Tags, Highlights. |
| **Coral** | `#FF6B6B` | `--color-coral` | `bg-coral`, `text-coral` | "Register" buttons, High-priority calls to action. |

### Semantic Mappings
These generic text utilities map to the specific colors above:
-   **Primary**: Mapped to **Oxford Blue**.
-   **Secondary**: Mapped to **Off-White**.
-   **Accent**: Mapped to **Electric Saffron**.

## 2. Typography

"Old School meets New School" - combining tradition with modern readability.

### Headings: Serif
-   **Font Family**: `Playfair Display`
-   **CSS Variable**: `--font-serif`
-   **Usage**: All headings (`h1` - `h6`). Mimics university letterheads and adds authority.

### Body/UI: Sans-Serif
-   **Font Family**: `Inter`
-   **CSS Variable**: `--font-sans`
-   **Usage**: Body text, UI elements, dates, times, speaker bios. Ensures high readability on mobile.

